<p>
<lb n="1"/>śakavarṣaṁbu <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> sarvvalōkāśraya śrīviṣṇuvarddha
<lb n="2" break="no"/>namahārājula pravarddhamāna vijayarājyadivya saṁvatsa <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>6 śrāhi dina 333 ṇḍa gaṁggagoṇḍacōḍavalanāṁṭi guddavādināṁṭi pe<unclear>ddaḍāka</unclear>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>rēmi śrībhīmēśvaramahādēvaraku vyatiyipāta nimittamunaṁ beddaḍāka <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/>madi pammiseṭṭi koḍku bhīmayayaina bhīmēśvaradhammiseṭṭi peṭṭina <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>lōhaAkhaṇḍavartti diviya Okkaṇḍaki dīniki nācaṁdrārkkamu neyi sariyi <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/>rugā śrībhīmēśvaramahādēvara kilaramuna prōlabōla nāvayayu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="8"/>ddibōla nāvayayuṁ bōtabhōla rājenayuṁ talarāśi nāvayayuṁ be
<lb n="9" break="no"/>raśina bōlunalvuruṁ būṁṭagāṁ brōlabōla nāvaya Aḍapuna Ayi <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="10"/>la kannani vasamunaṁ beṭṭina Inpa Eḍlu 50 nityapaḍi gola<supplied reason="omitted">va</supplied>ṁggala tri
<lb n="11" break="no"/>bhuvanāṁkusa nē māna 1 ḍakaremi rajēṁdracōḍaĀcaryyaḥ likhitaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

<p>2. In this and a few other cases ḍa is written without the <hi rend="italic">talakaṭṭu.</hi></p>

